{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"12":"Marriage (Kitab Al-Nikah)"},"section_detail":{"12":{"hadithnumber_first":2046,"hadithnumber_last":2174,"arabicnumber_first":2046,"arabicnumber_last":2174}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2070,"arabicnumber":2070,"text":"Le même récit a aussi été transmis par Ibn Abi Mulaikah. Il a dit : « ‘Ali رضي الله عنه est ensuite resté silencieux au sujet de ce mariage (c’est-à-dire épouser la fille d’Abu Jahl). »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (5230) Sahih Muslim (2449)"}],"reference":{"book":12,"hadith":25}}]}